               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000402-52-cd293" type="crimeDate">24th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000402-52-off292 t18000402-52-cd293"></join>, a pocket-book, value 1s. and seven duplicates, value 3d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18000402-52-victim431" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Illman
                        <interp inst="t18000402-52-victim431" type="surname" value="Illman"></interp>
